metadata.name: YuteDem #1
metadata.description: In our early days, the question " what do you want to be when you grow up?" arises provoking imagination on the most profound scale. Bypassing even the most obvious of barriers, we strive for achieving greatness. In the face of pure adversity, we can be anything. Within the imagination of the youth, nothing is impossible. The YuteDem explore this fearless hopefulness with the genesis on-chain collection of 25 pieces (erc721) embodying the childlike wonder of 'dreaming big'.
